00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:41.170
We know the Earth is round by observing it
closely.

00:00:41.170 --> 00:00:45.930
If you watch a ship as it disappears over
the horizon, the bottom vanishes first and

00:00:45.930 --> 00:00:47.649
